{"tid":2337750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求證 香港收容越南難民原因","createTime":"2020-12-23T13:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T13:43:08.000Z","uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"16162d87da264702f86c2c6e50603ac179638a71","tid":2337750,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"曾經聽過一啲老一輩既人講<br />\n證明唔到，但邏輯上合理，所以求高人指點<br />\n<br />\n佢話香港要收越南難民係中共連累<br />\n因為中共撐越共打南越<br />\n導致南越人道危機出現難民<br />\n港英初時都唔想拿屎上身<br />\n但係當時國際束手無策<br />\n唯有搵最接近既理由去搵人食死貓<br />\n支國當時係北韓式國家與世界無溝通<br />\n國際輿論唯有屈香港都係華人社會<br />\n逼香港幫支那(撐越共)既責任抹屎<br />\n搵香港食死貓<br />\n港英抵擋唔住先被逼將香港宣佈做第一收容港<br />\n<br />\n之後矮仔鄧又打越共<br />\n結果越南排華<br />\n又多一波難民潮<br />\n又係支共連累香港收難民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4f51c365764938498304ffbde28f20dd369fed","tid":2337750,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:52:35.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bb2cf23bca4f4a68afef9be537f20c185ab4b44a","tid":2337750,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"10918de18cd705588ea61e869a86beba66a35e9c","tid":2337750,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"80ec820699663ecc63d90cf17b703b37839a0f4c","tid":2337750,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"好似話係當初有個傳聞話非法入境香港既越南難民會特赦，所以先咁多人黎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記憶可能有錯"},{"pid":"9627ff29e74a2406687bf4c9b32a3a1210eba447","tid":2337750,"uid":75583,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"但我想講當日嘅越南難民 <br />\n9成9都係黃<br />\n好幾個孭住重charge 嘅手足都係越南裔"},{